Plugins:     StdFiles

Flag ui
  Description: enable build of curses interface

Library whiteengine
  Path: src/lib
  Modules: Types, Utils, Gametree, Position, Evaluation
  InternalModules: Apply_move, Check, Crc, Dna, Moves, Rules
  CompiledObject: native

Executable whitecamel
  Path:       src
  BuildDepends: whiteengine
  MainIs:     whitecamel.ml
  CompiledObject: native

Executable poseator
  if flag(ui)
    Build: true
  else
    Build: false
  Path:       src/tools
  MainIs:     poseator.ml
  BuildDepends: whiteengine, curses
  CompiledObject: native

Document whiteengine
  Title: "Whiteengine documentation"
  BuildTools+: ocamldoc
  XOCamlBuildPath: src/lib/
